snippet.title: Virtual Boy Longplay - Virtual Boy Wario Land (OLD)
snippet.description:
Important! There are in addition to the greyscale version 2 alternative versions of this Longplay for download on our website. A version in Virtual Boy Red and one in 3D. 

http://www.longplays.org 

Played By: T-0815

Virtual Boy Wario Land is a surprisingly good game. It has only one error. It was on Virtual Boy. ;)

Longplay includes: all treasures / best ending / most of the secrets

Level 01: 02:23 - Grotto Distress
Level 02: 06:40 - Guarded Prison
Level 03: 12:38 - Underwater Mayhem
Level 04: 19:52 - 1st Boss
Level 05: 23:53 - Crowded Forest
Level 06: 34:37 - Dangerous Waterfalls
Level 07: 47:09 - Quicksand Desert
Level 08: 59:45 - 2nd Boss
Level 09: 63:05 - Fruit Farm
Level 10: 73:55 - Spooky Mansion
Level 11: 82:15 - Machine Madness
Level 12: 92:58 - 3rd Boss
Level 13: 96:40 - Temple of Doom
Level 14: 104:15 - Final Boss -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
